    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="614"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d614">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 656.119/874</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Great Britain</hi> (<persName
                        corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_LIB1" type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Laughlin</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, [<date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 13, 1918</hi>
                        </date>.] <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received 6.20 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3682. War Trade Board [from <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_SLP1"
                        >Sheldon</persName>]:</p>
                <p>No. 1858. It is proposed to have a clause in general agreement by which Dutch
                    Government will recognize N[etherlands] O[versea] T[rust] agreement. Would the
                    following clause cover what you had in mind in Department’s 1708, October 1,
                    your 1322, so that you would be willing to participate with the Allied
                    Governments in the N. O. T. agreements should same meet with your approval as
                    finally drafted? If not, what changes do you desire? Please rush reply.</p>
                <quote rend="blockquote">
                    <p>The Netherlands Government will recognize the [<hi rend="italic">and?</hi>]
                        approve such agreement as may be made between British, French and Italian
                        Governments and the N. O. T. and also the participation therein by the
                        Government of the United States in such form as the last-named Government
                        may consider advisable. The Netherlands Government undertakes that the
                        existence of the N. O. T. shall continue during the currency of this
                        agreement.</p>
                </quote>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1918Supp01v01#p_LIB1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Laughlin</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
